<subSubSection id="15DE5FE0FFB4EF77FF12FBAEFAD1FB1A" pageId="28" pageNumber="29" type="description">
<paragraph id="5D7B0C6BFFB4EF77FF12FBAEFAD1FB1A" blockId="28.[151,1437,1051,1186]" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">
<materialsCitation id="EDAC0636FFB4EF77FF12FBAEFAD5FB1A" county="This" location="Mexican Transition Zone" municipality="Neotropical Region" pageId="28" pageNumber="29" specimenCount="1" stateProvince="Parana" typeStatus="syntype">
<collectingCounty id="B41A74E7FFB4EF77FF12FBAEFF7CFB8D" box="[151,201,1051,1077]" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">This</collectingCounty>
tribe is composed by 20 genera and 107 species distributed in the 
<collectingMunicipality id="BD1F9611FFB4EF77FC55FBAEFB07FB8D" box="[976,1202,1051,1077]" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">Neotropical Region</collectingMunicipality>
, 
<location id="581B5AB0FFB4EF77FB3AFBAEFF66FBE2" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:D56DBD7DFFB4EF77FF12FC66FAD1FB1A:581B5AB0FFB4EF77FB3AFBAEFF66FBE2" county="This" municipality="Neotropical Region" name="Mexican Transition Zone" pageId="28" pageNumber="29" stateProvince="Parana">Mexican Transition Zone</location>
, 
<location id="581B5AB0FFB4EF77FF5AFB8AFDFBFBE2" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:D56DBD7DFFB4EF77FF12FC66FAD1FB1A:581B5AB0FFB4EF77FF5AFB8AFDFBFBE2" box="[223,590,1087,1114]" county="This" municipality="Neotropical Region" name="South American Transition Zone" pageId="28" pageNumber="29" stateProvince="Parana">South American Transition Zone</location>
and 
<location id="581B5AB0FFB4EF77FD00FB8AFC86FBE1" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:D56DBD7DFFB4EF77FF12FC66FAD1FB1A:581B5AB0FFB4EF77FD00FB8AFC86FBE1" box="[645,819,1087,1113]" county="This" municipality="Neotropical Region" name="Neartic Region" pageId="28" pageNumber="29" stateProvince="Parana">Neartic Region</location>
. Most species within the tribe were described based on 
<typeStatus id="827FB2C9FFB4EF77FF12FBD1FF4CFBC6" box="[151,249,1124,1150]" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">syntypes</typeStatus>
and no taxonomic revisions had yet been made for taxa placed in 
<taxonomicName id="9AC477E8FFB4EF77FC66FBD6FB34FBC5" authorityName="Brunner von Wattenwyl" authorityYear="1878" box="[995,1153,1123,1149]" class="Insecta" family="Tettigoniidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="28" pageNumber="29" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="tribe" tribe="Microcentrini">Microcentrini</taxonomicName>
. The tribe is recorded for the first time in the 
<collectingRegion id="9F00C289FFB4EF77FEF6FB32FDB4FB19" box="[371,513,1159,1185]" country="Brazil" name="Parana" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">Paraná State</collectingRegion>
, with the recognition of five species within three genera in the ParNa Iguaçu
</materialsCitation>
.
</paragraph>
